        Try to reduce the depth of the scene tree by consolidating groups
        and transformations.

        The generic Graphics3d object can't be made flatter.

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: G = sage.plot.plot3d.base.Graphics3d()
            sage: G.flatten() is G
